'''苦槛蓝科'''共有3[[属|属]]约90[[种|种]]，生长在[[亚洲|亚洲]]、[[非洲|非洲]]、[[大洋洲|大洋洲]]和[[西印度群岛|西印度群岛]]。[[中国|中国]]只有1属，1种-[[苦槛蓝|苦槛蓝]]（''Myoporum bontioides'' (Sieb. et Zucc.) A. Gray），分布于东南沿海一带。

苦槛蓝科[[植物|植物]]大部分为[[灌木|灌木]]，也有[[乔木|乔木]]；单[[叶|叶]]互生；[[花|花]]两性，[[花萼|花萼]]5裂，[[花冠|花冠]]合瓣；[[果实|果实]]为[[核果|核果]]。<ref name="olmstead2001">{{cite journal | author = Olmstead, R. G., dePamphilis, C. W., Wolfe, A. D., Young, N. D., Elisons, W. J. & Reeves P. A. | title = Disintegration of the Scrophulariaceae | journal = American Journal of Botany | volume = 88 | pages = 348–361 | year = 2001 | url = http://www.amjbot.org/cgi/content/full/88/2/348 | doi = 10.2307/2657024 | pmid = 11222255 | access-date = 2008-12-02 | archive-date = 2010-06-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100626092426/http://www.amjbot.org/cgi/content/full/88/2/348 | dead-url = no }}</ref> 

